metadata.name: Intangible Touch 001
metadata.description:
An intangible touch, a dance of ethereal connections that defies the senses, transcending the boundaries of the physical. It whispers secrets beyond words, caressing our emotions and leaving indelible imprints upon our hearts.

In the language of silence, this mystic touch weaves threads of profound understanding, forging a bond that surpasses the limitations of our earthly existence.

It beckons us to embrace the unseen, to delve into the depths where meaning resides, reminding us that the intangible can hold the greatest power, and that our connection is felt in the realm beyond the tangible.


Concept, AI Collab & Digital Art by Mariela Di Nardo.
Dimensions 4000 x 6000 pixels.
